\b 4. List of variables in the file\
\

\b0 Henceforth when referring to "city", I refer to the the cities that were the head office of the 
\i Subd\'e9l\'e9gations
\i0 .\
\
ID: unique ID of each polygon.\
GENERALITE: categorical variable indicating to which 
\i G\'e9n\'e9ralit\'e9
\i0  the 
