\i0  belongs to.\
SUBDELEGAT: unique ID to identify the 
\i Subd\'e9l\'e9gation
\i0 .\
CITY_MAP: name of the city indicated on the digitized map.\
CODE_INSEE: code identifying the city in the Insee nomenclature.\
POSTE_CODE: postal code.\
CAPITAL: dummy variable indicating whether the 
\i Subd\'e9l\'e9gation
\i0  also host of the head office of the 
\i G\'e9n\'e9ralit\'e9
\i0 .\
COUNTRY: categorical variable indicating the country of belonging in 2014.\
